claim.claim-text:
1. A medical catheter, comprising: 
a body having a distal end portion comprising an expandable balloon, a distal wire port distal to the balloon, and a distal delivery port proximal to the balloon, and said body having a proximal end portion comprising a proximal inflation/wire port and a proximal delivery port; 
whrein said proximal inflation/wire port is fluidly coupled to said expandable balloon portion and to said distal wire port, and said proximal delivery port is fluidly coupled to said distal delivery port.
